{
  "texts": [
    "Here are some common methods and approaches used in this field.",
    "Gaikwad and Musande (2023) developed an advanced crop disease prediction technique using KNN, cetalatran optimization algorithm, and relief algorithm.",
    "The relief algorithm is used to select relevant features from high-resolution hyperspectral UV images by evaluating the strong dependencies and quality of attributes.",
    "In addition, it allocates a weight to each feature present in the training dataset and then selects the weighted features with the highest average relevance to crop disease prediction.",
    "The feature is measured using Boolean functions, integer numbers, or real values."
  ]
}